snippet.title: Need for Speed Accolades
snippet.description:
Discover the cars and customization of NFS: http://o.ea.com/44003
Get the Deluxe Edition to receive the BMW M3 E46 as a tricked out starter car: http://o.ea.com/41306

Tonight we Ride! Now available Worldwide.

What people are saying:
https://twitter.com/nmacipad/status/663489231457796096 
https://twitter.com/RozaaaWood1/status/662675552566968320 
https://twitter.com/Stefan24Frei/status/662404074139070464 
http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/need-for-speed-review/1900-6416300/
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3SJ9ccI2QP8 

Become an icon of urban car culture in Need for Speed. Race in and explore a huge nocturnal open world, express your style with authentic car customization and become immersed in a narrative staring real world icons like Magnus Walker and Ken Block.

Earn REP in the Five Ways to Play: http://bit.ly/1McaXsC

See all of the Need for Speed trailer's: http://bit.ly/1gGLucX

Join the NFS community for the latest news and game updates:

Twitter: http://bit.ly/1H3gpbR 
 
Facebook: http://on.fb.me/1DVSlTH 
 
Instagram: http://bit.ly/1RjBmVN 
 
YouTube: http://bit.ly/1InsHgG

If you want to keep racing on the go, Need for Speed No Limits is available now on mobile as a free download* in the App Store and Google Play. For more information about Need for Speed No Limits, please visit http://www.ea.com/needforspeednolimits.
